videos.description: With Oklahoma inbounding the ball from underneath the hoop, Jordan Woodard throws it up to Khadeem Lattin for the monster alley-oop jam.
videos.headline: Alley-oops off inbounds passes are always awesome

videos.description: Oklahoma shocks No. 7 West Virginia in Morgantown when Jordan Woodard hits the tough layup to break an 87-87 tie in overtime to give the Sooners the win.
videos.headline: Woodard's tough layup is the winner for Oklahoma
